<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">رَبَاب:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>لَهَا العُذْرُ مَنْ يَلْقَ أَحْبَابَهُ * بِهِمْ سَوْفَ يَنْسَى لِقَاءَ الصِّحَابْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
